==English==
===Phrasal verb===
'''[[kill]] [[two]] [[birds]] [[with]] [[one]] [[stone]]'''

#{{idiom}} to solve two problems at once
#:''Biking to work on a nice day '''kills two birds with one stone'''.  It makes both my commute and my workout more enjoyable.''

